481
00:43:37,783 --> 00:43:39,409
Move, shitbird!

482
00:43:43,330 --> 00:43:45,373
Jesus!

483
00:44:04,976 --> 00:44:08,146
Detective, my office.

484
00:44:42,097 --> 00:44:44,099
Yeah.

485
00:44:47,435 --> 00:44:48,937
Ooh!

486
