492
00:45:21,469 --> 00:45:24,347
An argument over a few cars?

493
00:45:24,431 --> 00:45:27,183
- That little polack?
- He's crazy, that one.

494
00:45:28,184 --> 00:45:31,229
The police have him now. So...

495
00:45:34,482 --> 00:45:36,443
The police still there?

496
00:45:38,111 --> 00:45:39,654
Go to the store.

497
00:45:40,363 --> 00:45:43,992
Whatever the police did not take,
papers, pictures, everything,

498
00:45:44,117 --> 00:45:45,785
you clean it up.

499
00:45:47,203 --> 00:45:50,290
The warehouse, too.
Everything gets clean now.

500
00:45:53,126 --> 00:45:54,502
Everything.

501
00:45:56,004 --> 00:45:58,423
And the phones are dead.

502
00:46:03,803 --> 00:46:06,890
Did you see that? They
just threw the phones.

503
00:46:08,350 --> 00:46:10,185
11-34 to surveillance.

504
00:46:10,894 --> 00:46:13,313
- Standing by.
- We got our man.

505
00:46:13,396 --> 00:46:16,775
Target number one is
a white male, 405, short,

506
00:46:16,858 --> 00:46:19,903
wearing a tan shirt and a grey tam.

507
00:46:20,862 --> 00:46:23,198
Copy your description.

508
00:46:23,865 --> 00:46:26,743
11-34 to surveillance,
both targets are on the move.

509
00:46:26,826 --> 00:46:29,245
We can't make the vehicle
but you sure as hell can.

510
00:46:29,329 --> 00:46:30,413
Copy.

511
00:46:30,497 --> 00:46:34,000
What was he doing
with that thing in his hand?

512
00:46:34,125 --> 00:46:36,211
Same thing you always do.

513
00:46:36,378 --> 00:46:40,131
Probably sending a text message.
My kids are crazy over that.

514
00:46:56,648 --> 00:46:58,608
That's our guy, right?

515
00:46:59,067 --> 00:47:02,570
What's-his-face sobotka
from the drug quarter?

516
00:47:10,745 --> 00:47:12,580
I need to get with vondas.

517
00:47:13,415 --> 00:47:15,250
Who's that?

518
00:47:20,422 --> 00:47:23,341
Spiros. Where is he?

519
00:47:24,467 --> 00:47:26,469
I don't know no spiros.

520
00:47:43,653 --> 00:47:46,698
- No shit.
- He just up and clocked him?

521
00:47:46,781 --> 00:47:49,868
- Daniels had everybody write what they saw.
- Even us suits.

522
00:47:49,951 --> 00:47:52,037
That was smart. Daniels is sharp.

523
00:47:52,120 --> 00:47:54,622
- Where's Prez now?
- Daniels took him home.

524
00:47:54,748 --> 00:47:58,043
- I don't think he'll come back here.
- You never know.

525
00:47:58,126 --> 00:48:01,629
He might have one of those psychological
bullshit things in his jacket

526
