in the last 24 hours.

588
00:52:03,705 --> 00:52:05,832
Exigent circumstances.

589
00:52:10,003 --> 00:52:11,504
Thanks, brother.

590
00:52:15,300 --> 00:52:18,219
Oh, fuck me.

591
00:52:20,430 --> 00:52:22,265
Nothing's easy.

592
00:52:25,268 --> 00:52:28,563
- What's up?
- They've dumped their phones.

593
00:52:29,230 --> 00:52:32,317
We're trying to get onto
the boss man's text messaging.

594
00:52:32,400 --> 00:52:33,985
Yeah?

595
00:52:34,068 --> 00:52:36,279
They sent that Greek mess over as email.

596
00:52:36,362 --> 00:52:38,865
After he inputs, the
computer will translate it.

597
00:52:38,948 --> 00:52:39,949
Got it.

598
00:52:43,494 --> 00:52:44,829
Shit.

599
00:52:58,593 --> 00:53:00,428
Hey, prissy.

600
00:53:02,096 --> 00:53:03,973
Thought you'd be here.

601
00:53:28,456 --> 00:53:30,416
Fucking Ziggy.

602
