606
00:53:44,639 --> 00:53:46,808
My mom's puke-yellow Chevy.

607
00:53:47,809 --> 00:53:49,602
We told him specifically,

608
00:53:49,685 --> 00:53:54,899
two bottles of pikesville rye and...

609
00:53:54,982 --> 00:53:57,568
Southern comfort for me.

610
00:54:02,198 --> 00:54:04,200
What did fucknuts get?

611
00:54:05,993 --> 00:54:07,787
Fucking Boone's farm.

612
00:54:12,417 --> 00:54:15,336
He said that's what the college kids drank.

613
00:54:16,087 --> 00:54:18,756
But we did it up. Right here.

614
00:54:20,299 --> 00:54:21,968
Yeah.

615
